apache module for realtime info service.

add to httpd.conf:

LoadModule rtinfo_module modules/mod_rtinfo.so
<Location /rtinfo>
SetHandler rtinfo
</Location> 

<IfModule mod_rtinfo.c>
RTSvc_Server_IP 192.168.1.137
RTSvc_Server_Port 9977
</IfModule>

KeepAlive on
MaxKeepAliveRequests 0
KeepAliveTimeout 15

<IfModule prefork.c>
StartServers 32
MinSpareServers 16
MaxSpareServers 64
ServerLimit 2048
MaxClients 1024
MaxRequestsPerChild 10000
</IfModule>

